I think the Synchmaster 910T has the same ddc
functions as the 912N. Therefore I added the file
"/usr/local/share/ddccontrol-db/monitor/SAM010F.xml",
containing:

-*-start-*-
<?xml version="1.0"?>
<!---The Samsung 910T is identical to 173P -->
<monitor include="SAM00D3" name="Samsung SyncMaster
910T"/>
-*-end-*-

